SubmitCashLedgerTransactionsForApproval is an ActionForm
    action is SubmitCashLedgerTransactionsForApproval
    title is "SubmitCashLedgerTransactionsForApproval"
    Layout
        single column
            visible when (TransactionApprovalCodeRequired)
                PrmApprovalCode
                    select is CashLedgerApprovalCodes
            PrmCommentText
                label is "Comment"
                use text area of 12 lines
